entries.journal_entry_completion_summary: You have successfully retrieved the pieces of broken translator for Jak Chucka.
entries.journal_entry_description: Jak's translator was broken into two pieces and taken by some Drennic Hunters and Guards. Collect the pieces.
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: Roughians known as the Drennics stole Jak Chucka's translator unit after breaking it into pieces. They are usually found in a bunker on Naboo.
entries.task02_journal_entry_description: You have successfully collected and rebuilt Jak's translator. Bring it to him near Theed.
entries.task03_journal_entry_description: One of the translator pieces was taken by Drennic Hunters.  Jak believes they patrol the area around a bunker in a heavily wooded area.
entries.task04_journal_entry_description: One of the translator pieces was taken by Drennic Guardians.  Jak believes they defend the Drennic's Bunker and are usually found inside.
